---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Wire Pegs"
  description="Wire Pegs are the original Australian stainless steel wire clothes peg. Selling quality pegs since 2015 with over 4,000 satisfied customers."
>

  <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-navy-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-500 mb-4">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy-900 leading-tight mb-6">About Wire Pegs</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">The original stainless steel wire clothes peg. Simple, durable, and built to last a lifetime.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Where it started</h2>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Wire Pegs are the original stainless steel wire clothes peg that have been sold in Australia since 2015. Today, we have the widest range including different strengths and lengths. Pegs for "windy" conditions are a slightly thicker wire than the Standard/Regular pegs and are stronger hold, but harder to squeeze.  "Easy squeeze" are a slightly thinner wire and suitable for those with reduced grip strength in their fingers. </p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">What started as a simple idea — a peg that actually lasts — has grown into a trusted brand with over 4,000 satisfied customers across the country.</p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The pegs are made in China at a trusted factory. 
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The concept is beautifully simple. A single piece of stainless steel wire, bent into the shape of a peg. No spring. No separate parts. Nothing to break, rust, or fail. Just a peg that works, year after year.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Why we exist</h2>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Australians throw away millions of plastic pegs every year. They snap, they rust, they stain clothes, and because they are unable to be recycled they end up in landfill. It's a problem hiding in plain sight in every Australian backyard.</p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Wire Pegs exist to offer a better alternative. Not a trendy eco product with a premium markup — just a genuinely better peg that happens to be far kinder to the environment because it lasts so much longer.</p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">One set of Wire Pegs replaces dozens of packs of plastic pegs over a lifetime. That's a small change with a real impact.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Where to buy</h2>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Wire Pegs are available through Biome — one of Australia's leading eco and sustainable living stores, with stores in Brisbane and Melbourne and online delivery nationwide.</p>
        <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Biome shares our values around quality, sustainability, and products that are built to last.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center border border-navy-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">2015</p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 text-sm">Year we started</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center border border-navy-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">4,000+</p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 text-sm">Happy customers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center border border-navy-100">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">3</p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 text-sm">Grades of stainless steel</p>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>